.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0b0710d891e3200f68d1ab5cd721ac7493f8ce80","tid":2089881,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88676ad8600d855ef281890647e41e059664a67e","tid":2089881,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:23:25.000Z","msg":"想知我有冇理解錯，將退休嘅人士，賣樓過去已有永住權，5+1轉BC。<br />\n<br />\n但因為冇交稅，冇當地福利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"睇埋要唔要過IELTS+life in the UK test再講啦"},{"pid":"38bb1f00b709f5a8520d57f30549ff264a2e6a5c","tid":2089881,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b0710d891e3200f68d1ab5cd721ac7493f8ce80","tid":2089881,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88676ad8600d855ef281890647e41e059664a67e","tid":2089881,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:23:25.000Z","msg":"想知我有冇理解錯，將退休嘅人士，賣樓過去已有永住權，5+1轉BC。<br />\n<br />\n但因為冇交稅，冇當地福利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"睇埋要唔要過IELTS+life in the UK test再講啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:30:24.000Z","msg":"life in the UK test點都要啦"},{"pid":"37d0d02168acb3e948a87a74b706a54bfc8e3739","tid":2089881,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7863cd7f210ca9aeec91987278a4f5f833065e8","tid":2089881,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d06050731d7e23ae753e4b245cb821bb2689ef3e","tid":2089881,"uid":180204,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88676ad8600d855ef281890647e41e059664a67e","tid":2089881,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:23:25.000Z","msg":"想知我有冇理